cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a deep learning model for traffic speed prediction using convolutional neural networks, which is a common approach in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The model also considers the impact of traffic volume, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the design of the model and its potential applications, which could be relevant to the categories of cryptography and security (cs.CR) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
